            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Identity Gateway</strong>
                <span>4 collectiona · 32 requesta</span>
                <a href="#" class="entity-link open-workspace-details" data-workspace-id="22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222">Workspace Details</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Billing Public API</strong>
                <span>3 collectiona · 27 requestova</span>
                <a href="#" class="entity-link open-workspace-details" data-workspace-id="33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333">Workspace Details</a>
            </li>
