        </div>
        <ul class="panel-list mono">
            <li><strong>Auth / Sessions</strong><span>GET, POST, DELETE</span><a class="entity-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Collection" asp-action="Details">Collection Details</a></li>
            <li><strong>Transactions</strong><span>POST, PATCH, GET</span><a class="entity-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Collection" asp-action="Details">Collection Details</a></li>
            <li><strong>Webhooks</strong><span>POST test payloads</span><a class="entity-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Collection" asp-action="Details">Collection Details</a></li>
